      "role": "user",
      "content": "specialists don't help. they just suggest more pills or harder stuff that makes me feel like a zombie. it's just a cycle of pain and then numbness. i'm just so done with the cycle. it feels like the only way to actually find some peace is to just... stop. to not have to wake up to this every single morning. does that even sound crazy? it feels like the most logical thing in the world.",
